<h1>Stage One</h1>

<p>In this stage, you get £1 in vouchers. The other pupil gets £0. You can give 
them some, none or all of your vouchers, in multiples of 10p.</p>

<p>Remember, if the computer picks you, your choice will decide how much
you and the other pupil get from this stage.</p>

<p>Please choose how much you will give the other pupil. Click 'Confirm' when 
you have made your decision.</p>

